  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant women having an uneventful single pregnancy and a female fetus diagnosed with
             anechoic ovarian cyst (diameter at least 30mm)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Multiple pregnancy

          -  Complicated pregnancy (PE, diabetes, PROM, fetal malformation)

          -  Echoic cyst (fluid debris level, septated, retracting clot, globally echoic)

          -  Unability to give informed consent
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
